| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7805 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8c25d845-c4c3-57c0-8117-18425cb5bade"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
